{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"The first thing I want to do is say thank you to all of you."},{"time":3000,"text":"The second thing I want to do is introduce my co-author"},{"time":6000,"text":"and dear friend and co-teacher."},{"time":8000,"text":"Ken and I have been working together"},{"time":10000,"text":"for almost 40 years."},{"time":12000,"text":"That's Ken Sharpe over there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":16000,"text":"So there is among many people --"},{"time":19000,"text":"certainly me and most of the people I talk to --"},{"time":21000,"text":"a kind of collective dissatisfaction"},{"time":24000,"text":"with the way things are working,"},{"time":26000,"text":"with the way our institutions run."},{"time":29000,"text":"Our kids' teachers seem to be failing them."},{"time":33000,"text":"Our doctors don't know who the hell we are,"},{"time":36000,"text":"and they don't have enough time for us."},{"time":38000,"text":"We certainly can't trust the bankers,"},{"time":40000,"text":"and we certainly can't trust the brokers."},{"time":43000,"text":"They almost brought the entire financial system down."},{"time":46000,"text":"And even as we do our own work,"},{"time":49000,"text":"all too often,"},{"time":51000,"text":"we find ourselves having to choose"},{"time":54000,"text":"between doing what we think is the right thing"},{"time":57000,"text":"and doing the expected thing,"},{"time":59000,"text":"or the required thing,"},{"time":61000,"text":"or the profitable thing."},{"time":63000,"text":"So everywhere we look,"},{"time":65000,"text":"pretty much across the board,"},{"time":67000,"text":"we worry that the people we depend on"},{"time":70000,"text":"don't really have our interests at heart."},{"time":74000,"text":"Or if they do have our interests at heart,"},{"time":77000,"text":"we worry that they don't know us well enough"},{"time":79000,"text":"to figure out what they need to do"},{"time":81000,"text":"in order to allow us"},{"time":83000,"text":"to secure those interests."},{"time":85000,"text":"They don't understand us."},{"time":87000,"text":"They don't have the time to get to know us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89000,"text":"There are two kinds of responses"},{"time":91000,"text":"that we make"},{"time":93000,"text":"to this sort of general dissatisfaction."},{"time":97000,"text":"If things aren't going right,"},{"time":99000,"text":"the first response is:"},{"time":101000,"text":"let's make more rules,"},{"time":103000,"text":"let's set up a set"},{"time":105000,"text":"of detailed procedures"},{"time":107000,"text":"to make sure that people will do the right thing."},{"time":110000,"text":"Give teachers scripts"},{"time":112000,"text":"to follow in the classroom,"},{"time":114000,"text":"so even if they don't know what they're doing"},{"time":116000,"text":"and don't care about the welfare of our kids,"},{"time":119000,"text":"as long as they follow the scripts,"},{"time":121000,"text":"our kids will get educated."},{"time":123000,"text":"Give judges a list of mandatory sentences"},{"time":126000,"text":"to impose for crimes,"},{"time":128000,"text":"so that you don't need to rely"},{"time":130000,"text":"on judges using their judgment."},{"time":133000,"text":"Instead, all they have to do"},{"time":135000,"text":"is look up on the list"},{"time":137000,"text":"what kind of sentence goes with what kind of crime."},{"time":140000,"text":"Impose limits"},{"time":142000,"text":"on what credit card companies can charge in interest"},{"time":145000,"text":"and on what they can charge in fees."},{"time":147000,"text":"More and more rules"},{"time":149000,"text":"to protect us"},{"time":151000,"text":"against an indifferent, uncaring"},{"time":153000,"text":"set of institutions we have to deal with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156000,"text":"Or -- or maybe and --"},{"time":158000,"text":"in addition to rules,"},{"time":160000,"text":"let's see if we can come up"},{"time":162000,"text":"with some really clever incentives"},{"time":164000,"text":"so that, even if the people we deal with"},{"time":166000,"text":"don't particularly want to serve our interests,"},{"time":169000,"text":"it is in their interest"},{"time":171000,"text":"to serve our interest --"},{"time":173000,"text":"the magic incentives"},{"time":175000,"text":"that will get people to do the right thing"},{"time":177000,"text":"even out of pure selfishness."},{"time":180000,"text":"So we offer teachers bonuses"},{"time":182000,"text":"if the kids they teach"},{"time":184000,"text":"score passing grades on these big test scores"},{"time":187000,"text":"that are used to evaluate"},{"time":189000,"text":"the quality of school systems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192000,"text":"Rules and incentives --"},{"time":194000,"text":"\"sticks\" and \"carrots.\""},{"time":196000,"text":"We passed a bunch of rules"},{"time":198000,"text":"to regulate the financial industry"},{"time":200000,"text":"in response to the recent collapse."},{"time":202000,"text":"There's the Dodd-Frank Act,"},{"time":204000,"text":"there's the new Consumer Financial Protection Agency"},{"time":207000,"text":"that is temporarily being headed through the backdoor"},{"time":210000,"text":"by Elizabeth Warren."},{"time":212000,"text":"Maybe these rules"},{"time":214000,"text":"will actually improve"},{"time":217000,"text":"the way these financial services companies behave."},{"time":221000,"text":"We'll see."},{"time":223000,"text":"In addition, we are struggling"},{"time":225000,"text":"to find some way to create incentives"},{"time":228000,"text":"for people in the financial services industry"},{"time":231000,"text":"that will have them more interested"},{"time":233000,"text":"in serving the long-term interests"},{"time":235000,"text":"even of their own companies,"},{"time":237000,"text":"rather than securing short-term profits."},{"time":241000,"text":"So if we find just the right incentives,"},{"time":243000,"text":"they'll do the right thing -- as I said -- selfishly,"},{"time":246000,"text":"and if we come up with the right rules and regulations,"},{"time":249000,"text":"they won't drive us all over a cliff."},{"time":252000,"text":"And Ken [Sharpe] and I certainly know"},{"time":255000,"text":"that you need to reign in the bankers."},{"time":258000,"text":"If there is a lesson to be learned from the financial collapse"},{"time":261000,"text":"it is that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263000,"text":"But what we believe,"},{"time":265000,"text":"and what we argue in the book,"},{"time":267000,"text":"is that there is no set of rules,"},{"time":270000,"text":"no matter how detailed,"},{"time":272000,"text":"no matter how specific,"},{"time":274000,"text":"no matter how carefully monitored"},{"time":276000,"text":"and enforced,"},{"time":278000,"text":"there is no set of rules"},{"time":280000,"text":"that will get us what we need."},{"time":282000,"text":"Why? Because bankers are smart people."},{"time":286000,"text":"And, like water,"},{"time":288000,"text":"they will find cracks"},{"time":290000,"text":"in any set of rules."},{"time":293000,"text":"You design a set of rules that will make sure"},{"time":296000,"text":"that the particular reason"},{"time":298000,"text":"why the financial system \"almost-collapse\""},{"time":300000,"text":"can't happen again."},{"time":302000,"text":"It is naive beyond description"},{"time":304000,"text":"to think that having blocked"},{"time":306000,"text":"this source of financial collapse,"},{"time":308000,"text":"you have blocked all possible sources of financial collapse."},{"time":311000,"text":"So it's just a question of waiting for the next one"},{"time":314000,"text":"and then marveling at how we could have been so stupid"},{"time":317000,"text":"as not to protect ourselves against that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320000,"text":"What we desperately need,"},{"time":322000,"text":"beyond, or along with, better rules"},{"time":325000,"text":"and reasonably smart incentives,"},{"time":327000,"text":"is we need virtue."},{"time":330000,"text":"We need character."},{"time":332000,"text":"We need people who want to do the right thing."},{"time":335000,"text":"And in particular,"},{"time":337000,"text":"the virtue that we need most of all"},{"time":340000,"text":"is the virtue that Aristotle called"},{"time":342000,"text":"\"practical wisdom.\""},{"time":345000,"text":"Practical wisdom"},{"time":347000,"text":"is the moral will"},{"time":349000,"text":"to do the right thing"},{"time":351000,"text":"and the moral skill"},{"time":353000,"text":"to figure out what the right thing is."},{"time":356000,"text":"So Aristotle was very interested in watching"},{"time":359000,"text":"how the craftsmen around him worked."},{"time":362000,"text":"And he was impressed"},{"time":364000,"text":"at how they would improvise"},{"time":366000,"text":"novel solutions to novel problems --"},{"time":368000,"text":"problems that they hadn't anticipated."},{"time":370000,"text":"So one example is he sees these stonemasons"},{"time":372000,"text":"working on the Isle of Lesbos,"},{"time":375000,"text":"and they need to measure out"},{"time":377000,"text":"round columns."},{"time":379000,"text":"Well if you think about it,"},{"time":381000,"text":"it's really hard to measure out round columns using a ruler."},{"time":384000,"text":"So what do they do?"},{"time":386000,"text":"They fashion a novel solution to the problem."},{"time":389000,"text":"They created a ruler that bends,"},{"time":392000,"text":"what we would call these days a tape measure --"},{"time":395000,"text":"a flexible rule,"},{"time":397000,"text":"a rule that bends."},{"time":399000,"text":"And Aristotle said,"},{"time":401000,"text":"\"Hah, they appreciated that sometimes"},{"time":404000,"text":"to design rounded columns,"},{"time":407000,"text":"you need to bend the rule.\""},{"time":410000,"text":"And Aristotle said"},{"time":412000,"text":"often in dealing with other people,"},{"time":415000,"text":"we need to bend the rules."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418000,"text":"Dealing with other people"},{"time":420000,"text":"demands a kind of flexibility"},{"time":423000,"text":"that no set of rules can encompass."},{"time":426000,"text":"Wise people know when and how"},{"time":428000,"text":"to bend the rules."},{"time":430000,"text":"Wise people know how to improvise."},{"time":433000,"text":"The way my co-author , Ken, and I talk about it,"},{"time":436000,"text":"they are kind of like jazz musicians."},{"time":438000,"text":"The rules are like the notes on the page,"},{"time":440000,"text":"and that gets you started,"},{"time":442000,"text":"but then you dance around the notes on the page,"},{"time":445000,"text":"coming up with just the right combination"},{"time":447000,"text":"for this particular moment"},{"time":449000,"text":"with this particular set of fellow players."},{"time":452000,"text":"So for Aristotle,"},{"time":454000,"text":"the kind"},{"time":457000,"text":"of rule-bending,"},{"time":460000,"text":"rule exception-finding and improvisation"},{"time":463000,"text":"that you see in skilled craftsmen"},{"time":465000,"text":"is exactly what you need"},{"time":467000,"text":"to be a skilled moral craftsman."},{"time":470000,"text":"And in interactions with people,"},{"time":472000,"text":"almost all the time,"},{"time":474000,"text":"it is this kind of flexibility that is required."},{"time":476000,"text":"A wise person knows when to bend the rules."},{"time":479000,"text":"A wise person knows when to improvise."},{"time":481000,"text":"And most important,"},{"time":483000,"text":"a wise person does this improvising and rule-bending"},{"time":486000,"text":"in the service of the right aims."},{"time":490000,"text":"If you are a rule-bender and an improviser"},{"time":493000,"text":"mostly to serve yourself,"},{"time":495000,"text":"what you get is ruthless manipulation of other people."},{"time":498000,"text":"So it matters that you do this wise practice"},{"time":500000,"text":"in the service of others"},{"time":502000,"text":"and not in the service of yourself."},{"time":504000,"text":"And so the will to do the right thing"},{"time":507000,"text":"is just as important as the moral skill"},{"time":509000,"text":"of improvisation"},{"time":511000,"text":"and exception-finding."},{"time":513000,"text":"Together they comprise practical wisdom,"},{"time":516000,"text":"which Aristotle thought"},{"time":518000,"text":"was the master virtue."}]},{"cues":[{"time":520000,"text":"So I'll give you an example"},{"time":522000,"text":"of wise practice in action."},{"time":524000,"text":"It's the case of Michael."},{"time":527000,"text":"Michael's a young guy."},{"time":529000,"text":"He had a pretty low-wage job."},{"time":531000,"text":"He was supporting his wife and a child,"},{"time":534000,"text":"and the child was going to parochial school."},{"time":536000,"text":"Then he lost his job."},{"time":539000,"text":"He panicked"},{"time":541000,"text":"about being able to support his family."},{"time":544000,"text":"One night, he drank a little too much,"},{"time":547000,"text":"and he robbed a cab driver --"},{"time":549000,"text":"stole 50 dollars."},{"time":551000,"text":"He robbed him at gunpoint."},{"time":553000,"text":"It was a toy gun."},{"time":556000,"text":"He got caught. He got tried."},{"time":559000,"text":"He got convicted."},{"time":561000,"text":"The Pennsylvania sentencing guidelines"},{"time":564000,"text":"required a minimum sentence for a crime like this"},{"time":567000,"text":"of two years, 24 months."},{"time":569000,"text":"The judge on the case, Judge Lois Forer"},{"time":572000,"text":"thought that this made no sense."},{"time":575000,"text":"He had never committed a crime before."},{"time":578000,"text":"He was a responsible husband and father."},{"time":581000,"text":"He had been faced with desperate circumstances."},{"time":583000,"text":"All this would do is wreck a family."},{"time":586000,"text":"And so she improvised a sentence -- 11 months,"},{"time":589000,"text":"and not only that,"},{"time":591000,"text":"but release every day to go to work."},{"time":593000,"text":"Spend your night in jail, spend your day holding down a job."},{"time":596000,"text":"He did. He served out his sentence."},{"time":599000,"text":"He made restitution"},{"time":601000,"text":"and found himself a new job."},{"time":603000,"text":"And the family was united."}]},{"cues":[{"time":606000,"text":"And it seemed on the road"},{"time":608000,"text":"to some sort of a decent life --"},{"time":611000,"text":"a happy ending to a story"},{"time":614000,"text":"involving wise improvisation"},{"time":616000,"text":"from a wise judge."},{"time":619000,"text":"But it turned out"},{"time":622000,"text":"the prosecutor was not happy"},{"time":625000,"text":"that Judge Forer ignored the sentencing guidelines"},{"time":628000,"text":"and sort of invented her own,"},{"time":630000,"text":"and so he appealed."},{"time":633000,"text":"And he asked for the mandatory minimum sentence"},{"time":636000,"text":"for armed robbery."},{"time":638000,"text":"He did after all have a toy gun."},{"time":641000,"text":"The mandatory minimum sentence for armed robbery"},{"time":643000,"text":"is five years."},{"time":646000,"text":"He won the appeal."},{"time":648000,"text":"Michael was sentenced to five years in prison."},{"time":652000,"text":"Judge Forer had to follow the law."},{"time":656000,"text":"And by the way, this appeal went through"},{"time":658000,"text":"after he had finished serving his sentence,"},{"time":660000,"text":"so he was out and working at a job"},{"time":663000,"text":"and taking care of his family"},{"time":665000,"text":"and he had to go back into jail."},{"time":667000,"text":"Judge Forer did what she was required to do,"},{"time":670000,"text":"and then she quit the bench."},{"time":674000,"text":"And Michael disappeared."},{"time":678000,"text":"So that is an example,"},{"time":680000,"text":"both of wisdom in practice"},{"time":682000,"text":"and the subversion of wisdom"},{"time":684000,"text":"by rules that are meant, of course, to make things better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":687000,"text":"Now consider Ms. Dewey."},{"time":689000,"text":"Ms. Dewey's a teacher in a Texas elementary school."},{"time":692000,"text":"She found herself listening to a consultant one day"},{"time":695000,"text":"who was trying to help teachers"},{"time":697000,"text":"boost the test scores of the kids,"},{"time":699000,"text":"so that the school"},{"time":701000,"text":"would reach the elite category"},{"time":704000,"text":"in percentage of kids passing big tests."},{"time":706000,"text":"All these schools in Texas compete with one another"},{"time":708000,"text":"to achieve these milestones,"},{"time":710000,"text":"and there are bonuses and various other treats"},{"time":713000,"text":"that come if you beat the other schools."},{"time":716000,"text":"So here was the consultant's advice:"},{"time":719000,"text":"first, don't waste your time on kids"},{"time":722000,"text":"who are going to pass the test no matter what you do."},{"time":726000,"text":"Second, don't waste your time"},{"time":728000,"text":"on kids who can't pass the test"},{"time":731000,"text":"no matter what you do."},{"time":733000,"text":"Third, don't waste your time"},{"time":735000,"text":"on kids who moved into the district"},{"time":738000,"text":"too late for their scores to be counted."},{"time":741000,"text":"Focus all of your time and attention"},{"time":744000,"text":"on the kids who are on the bubble,"},{"time":747000,"text":"the so-called \"bubble kids\" --"},{"time":749000,"text":"kids where your intervention"},{"time":751000,"text":"can get them just maybe over the line"},{"time":753000,"text":"from failing to passing."},{"time":755000,"text":"So Ms. Dewey heard this,"},{"time":757000,"text":"and she shook her head in despair"},{"time":760000,"text":"while fellow teachers were sort of cheering each other on"},{"time":763000,"text":"and nodding approvingly."},{"time":765000,"text":"It's like they were about to go play a football game."},{"time":767000,"text":"For Ms. Dewey,"},{"time":769000,"text":"this isn't why she became a teacher."}]},{"cues":[{"time":772000,"text":"Now Ken and I are not naive,"},{"time":774000,"text":"and we understand that you need to have rules."},{"time":777000,"text":"You need to have incentives."},{"time":779000,"text":"People have to make a living."},{"time":781000,"text":"But the problem"},{"time":783000,"text":"with relying on rules and incentives"},{"time":785000,"text":"is that they demoralize"},{"time":788000,"text":"professional activity,"},{"time":790000,"text":"and they demoralize professional activity"},{"time":792000,"text":"in two senses."},{"time":794000,"text":"First, they demoralize the people"},{"time":796000,"text":"who are engaged in the activity."},{"time":798000,"text":"Judge Forer quits,"},{"time":800000,"text":"and Ms. Dewey in completely disheartened."},{"time":802000,"text":"And second,"},{"time":804000,"text":"they demoralize the activity itself."},{"time":806000,"text":"The very practice is demoralized,"},{"time":809000,"text":"and the practitioners are demoralized."},{"time":811000,"text":"It creates people --"},{"time":813000,"text":"when you manipulate incentives to get people to do the right thing --"},{"time":816000,"text":"it creates people"},{"time":818000,"text":"who are addicted to incentives."},{"time":820000,"text":"That is to say, it creates people"},{"time":822000,"text":"who only do things for incentives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":824000,"text":"Now the striking thing about this"},{"time":826000,"text":"is that psychologists have known this"},{"time":828000,"text":"for 30 years."},{"time":830000,"text":"Psychologists have known"},{"time":832000,"text":"about the negative consequences of incentivizing everything"},{"time":835000,"text":"for 30 years."},{"time":837000,"text":"We know that if you reward kids for drawing pictures,"},{"time":840000,"text":"they stop caring about the drawing"},{"time":842000,"text":"and care only about the reward."},{"time":844000,"text":"If you reward kids for reading books,"},{"time":846000,"text":"they stop caring about what's in the books"},{"time":849000,"text":"and only care about how long they are."},{"time":851000,"text":"If you reward teachers for kids' test scores,"},{"time":854000,"text":"they stop caring about educating"},{"time":856000,"text":"and only care about test preparation."},{"time":858000,"text":"If you were to reward doctors"},{"time":860000,"text":"for doing more procedures --"},{"time":862000,"text":"which is the current system -- they would do more."},{"time":864000,"text":"If instead you reward doctors for doing fewer procedures,"},{"time":867000,"text":"they will do fewer."},{"time":869000,"text":"What we want, of course,"},{"time":871000,"text":"is doctors who do just the right amount of procedures"},{"time":873000,"text":"and do the right amount for the right reason --"},{"time":876000,"text":"namely, to serve the welfare of their patients."},{"time":879000,"text":"Psychologists have known this for decades,"},{"time":881000,"text":"and it's time for policymakers"},{"time":884000,"text":"to start paying attention"},{"time":886000,"text":"and listen to psychologists a little bit,"},{"time":889000,"text":"instead of economists."}]},{"cues":[{"time":892000,"text":"And it doesn't have to be this way."},{"time":894000,"text":"We think, Ken and I, that there are real sources of hope."},{"time":897000,"text":"We identify one set of people"},{"time":899000,"text":"in all of these practices"},{"time":901000,"text":"who we call canny outlaws."},{"time":903000,"text":"These are people"},{"time":905000,"text":"who, being forced to operate"},{"time":908000,"text":"in a system that demands rule-following"},{"time":910000,"text":"and creates incentives,"},{"time":912000,"text":"find away around the rules,"},{"time":914000,"text":"find a way to subvert the rules."},{"time":917000,"text":"So there are teachers who have these scripts to follow,"},{"time":919000,"text":"and they know that if they follow these scripts, the kids will learn nothing."},{"time":922000,"text":"And so what they do is they follow the scripts,"},{"time":925000,"text":"but they follow the scripts at double-time"},{"time":928000,"text":"and squirrel away little bits of extra time"},{"time":931000,"text":"during which they teach in the way"},{"time":933000,"text":"that they actually know is effective."},{"time":936000,"text":"So these are little ordinary, everyday heroes,"},{"time":939000,"text":"and they're incredibly admirable,"},{"time":941000,"text":"but there's no way that they can sustain this kind of activity"},{"time":944000,"text":"in the face of a system"},{"time":946000,"text":"that either roots them out"},{"time":948000,"text":"or grinds them down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":950000,"text":"So canny outlaws are better than nothing,"},{"time":952000,"text":"but it's hard to imagine any canny outlaw"},{"time":954000,"text":"sustaining that for an indefinite period of time."},{"time":957000,"text":"More hopeful"},{"time":959000,"text":"are people we call system-changers."},{"time":961000,"text":"These are people who are looking"},{"time":963000,"text":"not to dodge the system's rules and regulations,"},{"time":966000,"text":"but to transform the system,"},{"time":968000,"text":"and we talk about several."},{"time":970000,"text":"One in particular"},{"time":972000,"text":"is a judge named Robert Russell."},{"time":975000,"text":"And one day he was faced"},{"time":977000,"text":"with the case of Gary Pettengill."},{"time":980000,"text":"Pettengill was a 23-year-old vet"},{"time":983000,"text":"who had planned to make the army a career,"},{"time":985000,"text":"but then he got a severe back injury in Iraq,"},{"time":987000,"text":"and that forced him to take a medical discharge."},{"time":990000,"text":"He was married, he had a third kid on the way,"},{"time":993000,"text":"he suffered from PTSD, in addition to the bad back,"},{"time":996000,"text":"and recurrent nightmares,"},{"time":998000,"text":"and he had started using marijuana"},{"time":1000000,"text":"to ease some of the symptoms."},{"time":1003000,"text":"He was only able to get part-time work because of his back,"},{"time":1006000,"text":"and so he was unable to earn enough to put food on the table"},{"time":1009000,"text":"and take care of his family."},{"time":1011000,"text":"So he started selling marijuana."},{"time":1013000,"text":"He was busted in a drug sweep."},{"time":1016000,"text":"His family was kicked out of their apartment,"},{"time":1018000,"text":"and the welfare system"},{"time":1020000,"text":"was threatening to take away his kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1022000,"text":"Under normal sentencing procedures,"},{"time":1024000,"text":"Judge Russell would have had little choice"},{"time":1027000,"text":"but to sentence Pettengill to serious jail-time"},{"time":1029000,"text":"as a drug felon."},{"time":1032000,"text":"But Judge Russell did have an alternative."},{"time":1035000,"text":"And that's because he was in a special court."},{"time":1038000,"text":"He was in a court called the Veterans' Court."},{"time":1041000,"text":"In the Veterans' Court --"},{"time":1043000,"text":"this was the first of its kind in the United States."},{"time":1046000,"text":"Judge Russell created the Veterans' Court."},{"time":1048000,"text":"It was a court only for veterans"},{"time":1050000,"text":"who had broken the law."},{"time":1053000,"text":"And he had created it exactly because"},{"time":1055000,"text":"mandatory sentencing laws"},{"time":1057000,"text":"were taking the judgment out of judging."},{"time":1060000,"text":"No one wanted non-violent offenders --"},{"time":1063000,"text":"and especially non-violent offenders who were veterans to boot --"},{"time":1066000,"text":"to be thrown into prison."},{"time":1068000,"text":"They wanted to do something about what we all know,"},{"time":1071000,"text":"namely the revolving door of the criminal justice system."},{"time":1074000,"text":"And what the Veterans' Court did,"},{"time":1076000,"text":"was it treated each criminal as an individual,"},{"time":1079000,"text":"tried to get inside their problems,"},{"time":1082000,"text":"tried to fashion responses to their crimes"},{"time":1085000,"text":"that helped them to rehabilitate themselves,"},{"time":1087000,"text":"and didn't forget about them once the judgment was made."},{"time":1090000,"text":"Stayed with them, followed up on them,"},{"time":1093000,"text":"made sure that they were sticking to whatever plan"},{"time":1095000,"text":"had been jointly developed"},{"time":1097000,"text":"to get them over the hump."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1099000,"text":"There are now 22 cities"},{"time":1101000,"text":"that have Veterans' Courts like this."},{"time":1103000,"text":"Why has the idea spread?"},{"time":1106000,"text":"Well, one reason is"},{"time":1108000,"text":"that Judge Russell"},{"time":1110000,"text":"has now seen 108 vets"},{"time":1112000,"text":"in his Veterans' Court"},{"time":1114000,"text":"as of February of this year,"},{"time":1116000,"text":"and out of 108,"},{"time":1118000,"text":"guess how many have gone back through"},{"time":1120000,"text":"the revolving door of justice"},{"time":1122000,"text":"into prison."},{"time":1124000,"text":"None. None."},{"time":1126000,"text":"Anyone would glom onto"},{"time":1129000,"text":"a criminal justice system"},{"time":1131000,"text":"that has this kind of a record."},{"time":1133000,"text":"So here's is a system-changer, and it seems to be catching."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1136000,"text":"There's a banker"},{"time":1138000,"text":"who created a for-profit community bank"},{"time":1140000,"text":"that encouraged bankers -- I know this is hard to believe --"},{"time":1143000,"text":"encouraged bankers who worked there to do well"},{"time":1146000,"text":"by doing good for their low-income clients."},{"time":1149000,"text":"The bank helped finance the rebuilding"},{"time":1152000,"text":"of what was otherwise a dying community."},{"time":1155000,"text":"Though their loan recipients were high-risk by ordinary standards,"},{"time":1158000,"text":"the default rate was extremely low."},{"time":1161000,"text":"The bank was profitable."},{"time":1164000,"text":"The bankers stayed with their loan recipients."},{"time":1166000,"text":"They didn't make loans and then sell the loans."},{"time":1168000,"text":"They serviced the loans."},{"time":1170000,"text":"They made sure that their loan recipients"},{"time":1172000,"text":"were staying up with their payments."},{"time":1175000,"text":"Banking hasn't always been"},{"time":1178000,"text":"the way we read about it now in the newspapers."},{"time":1182000,"text":"Even Goldman Sachs"},{"time":1184000,"text":"once used to serve clients,"},{"time":1187000,"text":"before it turned into an institution"},{"time":1190000,"text":"that serves only itself."},{"time":1192000,"text":"Banking wasn't always this way,"},{"time":1194000,"text":"and it doesn't have to be this way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1199000,"text":"So there are examples like this in medicine --"},{"time":1202000,"text":"doctors at Harvard"},{"time":1204000,"text":"who are trying to transform medical education,"},{"time":1206000,"text":"so that you don't get a kind of ethical erosion"},{"time":1208000,"text":"and loss of empathy,"},{"time":1210000,"text":"which characterizes most medical students"},{"time":1212000,"text":"in the course of their medical training."},{"time":1214000,"text":"And the way they do it is to give third-year medical students"},{"time":1217000,"text":"patients who they follow for an entire year."},{"time":1219000,"text":"So the patients are not organ systems,"},{"time":1221000,"text":"and they're not diseases;"},{"time":1223000,"text":"they're people, people with lives."},{"time":1225000,"text":"And in order to be an effective doctor,"},{"time":1227000,"text":"you need to treat people who have lives and not just disease."},{"time":1230000,"text":"In addition to which there's an enormous amount of back and forth,"},{"time":1233000,"text":"mentoring of one student by another,"},{"time":1235000,"text":"of all the students by the doctors,"},{"time":1238000,"text":"and the result is a generation -- we hope -- of doctors"},{"time":1241000,"text":"who do have time for the people they treat."},{"time":1243000,"text":"We'll see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1245000,"text":"So there are lots of examples like this that we talk about."},{"time":1248000,"text":"Each of them shows that it is possible"},{"time":1250000,"text":"to build on and nurture character"},{"time":1253000,"text":"and keep a profession"},{"time":1255000,"text":"true to its proper mission --"},{"time":1257000,"text":"what Aristotle would have called its proper telos."},{"time":1261000,"text":"And Ken and I believe"},{"time":1263000,"text":"that this is what practitioners actually want."},{"time":1266000,"text":"People want to be allowed"},{"time":1268000,"text":"to be virtuous."},{"time":1270000,"text":"They want to have permission to do the right thing."},{"time":1273000,"text":"They don't want to feel"},{"time":1275000,"text":"like they need to take a shower"},{"time":1277000,"text":"to get the moral grime off their bodies everyday"},{"time":1280000,"text":"when they come home from work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1283000,"text":"Aristotle thought that practical wisdom"},{"time":1285000,"text":"was the key to happiness,"},{"time":1287000,"text":"and he was right."},{"time":1290000,"text":"There's now a lot of research being done in psychology"},{"time":1293000,"text":"on what makes people happy,"},{"time":1295000,"text":"and the two things that jump out in study after study --"},{"time":1298000,"text":"I know this will come as a shock to all of you --"},{"time":1300000,"text":"the two things that matter most to happiness"},{"time":1303000,"text":"are love and work."},{"time":1306000,"text":"Love: managing successfully"},{"time":1309000,"text":"relations with the people who are close to you"},{"time":1311000,"text":"and with the communities of which you are a part."},{"time":1314000,"text":"Work: engaging in activities"},{"time":1317000,"text":"that are meaningful and satisfying."},{"time":1320000,"text":"If you have that, good close relations with other people,"},{"time":1323000,"text":"work that's meaningful and fulfilling,"},{"time":1326000,"text":"you don't much need anything else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1329000,"text":"Well, to love well and to work well,"},{"time":1332000,"text":"you need wisdom."},{"time":1334000,"text":"Rules and incentives don't tell you"},{"time":1336000,"text":"how to be a good friend, how to be a good parent,"},{"time":1339000,"text":"how to be a good spouse,"},{"time":1341000,"text":"or how to be a good doctor or a good lawyer"},{"time":1343000,"text":"or a good teacher."},{"time":1345000,"text":"Rules and incentives"},{"time":1347000,"text":"are no substitutes for wisdom."},{"time":1349000,"text":"Indeed, we argue,"},{"time":1351000,"text":"there is no substitute for wisdom."},{"time":1354000,"text":"And so practical wisdom"},{"time":1356000,"text":"does not require"},{"time":1358000,"text":"heroic acts of self-sacrifice"},{"time":1361000,"text":"on the part of practitioners."},{"time":1364000,"text":"In giving us the will and the skill"},{"time":1366000,"text":"to do the right thing -- to do right by others --"},{"time":1369000,"text":"practical wisdom also gives us"},{"time":1371000,"text":"the will and the skill"},{"time":1373000,"text":"to do right by ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1376000,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1378000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}